How many of us had to bluff our way through the first gatekeeper on tech support like this?<p><pre><code>   Tech: &quot;Could you please unplug your computer for 20 seconds and restart it?&quot;
   Me: &quot;Okay. <does nothing for 60 seconds>.  Okay, it&#x27;s back&quot;
</code></pre>
Or this gem?<p><pre><code>   Tech: &quot;What browser are you using?&quot;
   Me: &quot;<Looks at Ubuntu desktop>  Internet Explorer 6&quot;.</code></pre>
